2661, "content_length": 89, "reply_to": 868748254, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779256387}, {"pid": 868750283, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868749777,45974302,5492]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60436766]稲橋[/uid] (2026-05-20 14:00):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大机器人版块也做完双头了。一波流结束了吗？[s:ac:哭1]<br/>以为这次能和算力齐头并进一下，最早做出个底分型走长一点[/quote]<br/>我觉得差不多没了  机器人这波换了个名字  叫什么物理AI  然后吹了一波 最强也是快速做完双头也没什么力了 双头的票比航天少", "lou": 2662, "content_length": 113, "reply_to": 868749777, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779257061}, {"pid": 868750868, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868750368,45974302,5493]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62740939]一口糖汽水[/uid] (2026-05-20 14:05):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]今天不拉光主要可能还是怕晚上英伟达的财报吧，在财报落地前，光的不确定性太高[/quote]<br/>对", "lou": 2663, "content_length": 7, "reply_to": 868750368, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779257341}, {"pid": 868751263, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 49, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868750985,45974302,5494]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-05-20 14:09):[/b]<br/><br/>上次小英miss了，这次大英不太可能miss吧[s:a2:doge][/quote]<br/>无所谓 只要不是超超超预期 大概率都是先砸 然后开始诱多接力半导体 让半导体那边休息一下", "lou": 2664, "content_length": 85, "reply_to": 868750985, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779257528}, {"pid": 868751863, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 82, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "更新一下宏观<br/>之前我判断的 石油会维持一段100-110的价格  目的是给川普卖油  已经达成<br/>目前我判断，这个时间将会结束，后续会下跌。时间节点看美联储换人后第一次会议附近时间。", "lou": 2665, "content_length": 159, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779257800}, {"pid": 868753708, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 118, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天全天没有任何买点  全天黄线在下 还放量<br/>相反很多科技票到了我的止盈区间 我按计划该出的都出了。<br/>出来的钱不会马上进去的。如果沃什上台能来个普跌 打出C底，那我才会考虑场外调回资金买 不然没差价 没意思。", "lou": 2666, "content_length": 189, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779258628}, {"pid": 868754899, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868754534,45974302,5498]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-05-20 14:36):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，本周五沃什上任，6月中第一次议息。是不是认为3-5的高点会在议息前到来。不管议息结果如何，都会接机开启大4浪呢？[s:pst:音乐][s:pst:音乐][/quote]<br/>我算不到那么远 但是每一次新主席上台后续大概率回撤  按老美回撤10%-15% 我们这边应该不会走独立行情吧<br/>这是历史经验  我决定正常避让", "lou": 2667, "content_length": 124, "reply_to": 868754534, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779259167}, {"pid": 868755049, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 46, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868754836,45974302,5499]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=40951992]夜宿秋风[/uid] (2026-05-20 14:38):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，模组的加速预期是要等c杀后才会有吗[s:ac:羡慕][/quote]<br/>原厂带模组走模组的最后一波吧 我感觉应该是这样。", "lou": 2668, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 868754836, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779259244}, {"pid": 868756779, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 31, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868756209,45974302,5501]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67018579]a315270319[/uid] (2026-05-20 14:49):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大看过氟化工吗，当成半导体材料处理？[/quote]<br/>DFD那种吗？那个是  电子级轻氟酸 概念  属于半导体材料涨价<br/>上周开始吹的。我这边上周末收到的消息。", "lou": 2669, "content_length": 94, "reply_to": 868756209, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779259999}, {"pid": 868756981, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 76, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 14:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868756494,45974302,5501]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60068117]孤寂的刀锋[/uid] (2026-05-20 14:51):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，假如这轮C杀调整完成。后续依然走3-5的后半程的话，你看好哪些板块？依然是半导体吗？[/quote]<br/>怎么 又想抢我先手吗？<br/>我有些东西输出还是太超前了 <br/>确实不适合你们  你可以问问楼里的", "lou": 2670, "content_length": 81, "reply_to": 868756494, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779260085}, {"pid": 868758265, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 59, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 15:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868758008,45974302,5504]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1134755]icyphoenix[/uid] (2026-05-20 15:02):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大上次被抢先手已经骂了两遍了 XXXXXXXXXXXXX[/quote]<br/>你就说我骂得对不对吧", "lou": 2671, "content_length": 25, "reply_to": 868758008, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779260621}, {"pid": 868758385, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 89, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 15:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "如果你们不记得上一次怎么套山顶亏下来的 <br/>我建议回顾一下我上一次出机器人之后的样子", "lou": 2672, "content_length": 78, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779260673}, {"pid": 868762472, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 42, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 15:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868762011,45974302,5507]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67177418]小蝎子ICE二代[/uid] (2026-05-20 15:29):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，劳动节后没见您提过游戏了<br/>请问这个板块是和ai软一样出了吗？[/quote]<br/>游戏当时出了  资金和AI软合并  然后之后AI软也不做了 <br/>当时还是判断被虹吸  所以低位没涨的非半导体反而更危险。", "lou": 2673, "content_length": 103, "reply_to": 868762011, "from_client": "0 